text: Bischofszell is a municipality of the district of Weinfelden in the canton of Thurgau in the country of Switzerland. It has a population of 5,500 people. The local industry is Bischofszell Konserven. It now belongs to Migros. They make jams, fruit juices, various cans, convenience food, among them Anna's Best. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Municipalities in Weinfelden Category:Cities in Switzerland
